attachments.title: #FutureHive Memes Are Taking Over Twitter
attachments.text: Twitter is amazing sometimes. It’s without question Future is on a ridiculous Stephen Curry-like rampage right now. After releasing his album Honest to mixed reviews, and breaking up with Ciara (just saying), he’s been three for three with his latest mixtapes. Monster, Beast Mode and 56 Nights all inclide top notch production from Metro Boomin, Zaytoven, and 808 Mafia and a plethora of hits. There is something unearthly with his... Read more »
